tention','1','1249442407SINU'),('Online Status','1','1251084122MTBZ'),('If yes, a confirmation email sent to the author of the ticket after a ticket is successfully saved.','1','1251087468IYER'),('If yes, an email is sent to the author of a ticket to notify that the moderator or support replied to the ticket.<br>','1','1251087468IYES'),('If yes, the assigned moderator of the project where the ticket belongs can receive an email notification when a new a ticket or areply is created.<br>','1','1251087468IYET'),('If yes,the creator of the reply will receive an email which is a copy of reply that he/she created.','1','1251087468IYEU'),('To assigned moderators','1','1251087468IYEV'),('Ticket #','1','1251087469EETU'),('On Creation','1','1251087469EETV'),('On Replies','1','1251087469EETW'),('To assigned moderator','1','1251087469EETX'),('View Tickets','1','1251087473QQLF'),('This listing views all the tickets you submitted.<br><ul><li>Before creating a new ticket, please <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">check if there is already an existing ticket</span> that has addressed your concerns. You can only create a new ticket if your concerns haven\'t been addressed yet.</li><li>To see the replies of the ticket created, just click on the ticket title.</li></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 255);\">More Information:</span> When searching for information in a listing, you can use keywords like the name key or title of the ticket. You can also automatically sort a listing by ticket type or category.','1','1251087477HEHD'),('To create a new canned reply, complete the fields asked:<br><ul><li>Title - the name of the canned reply.</li><li>Category - what category does this canned reply belongs.</li><li>Type - in what type of question does this canned reply belongs to.</li><li>Private - accessible only for the moderators.</li><li>Content - the content or description of the canned reply.</li></ul><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(51, 0, 255);\">NOTE:</span><br><ul><li>You can also create notes here, by making the canned reply as private so that only moderators can access it.<br></li></ul>','1','1251087478TJMO'),('This page allows you to set the notifications of each category.<br><br><ul><li>On Creation, an email confirmation will be sent to the author of the ticket.<br></li><li>On Replies, an email notification will be sent to the author of the reply when the support replied..</li><li>To assigned Moderator, an email is send to the assigned moderators to that category if and only if the moderator wants to receive a notification.</li><li>Send Copy, the creator of the reply will receive an email which is a copy of reply that he/she created.</li></ul>','1','1251087478TJMP'),('Customer\'s Listing','1','1251087478TJMQ'),('To Create Canned Reply','1','1251087478TJMR'),('Notification Settings','1','1251087478TJMS'),('Specify the time after which a ticket is considered late reply.<br><div>Unit in hours.</div>','1','1251253275MFSY'),('Email account of the sender to be used.<br>','1','1251253275MFSZ'),('Email account to be used where the email messages are sent to by the customers.<br>','1','1251253275MFTA'),('Automatic conversion of reply','1','1251253275MFTB'),('Bounceback Email','1','1251253275MFTC'),('Unpaid','1','1251298684SHUF'),('Solved','1','1251298684SHUG'),('Automatic assignment of moderator','1','1251364186BXWE'),('Allow non-registered','1','1251534828ITXB'),('If yes, non-registered users are allow to submit a ticket.<br>Else, only registered users can submit a ticket.<br>','1','1251770734GTUD'),('Use Comment System?','1','1251799425OCEW'),('Ticket ID: $ID','1','1253277991HEPH'),('Email Information','1','1253277998HJXE'),('Moderators','1','1253278002FXNZ'),('Use this view to assign or unassign moderators to a category:<br><br><ul><li>To assign or unassign a member, click the link under the column Assigned. The text link will change from <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 51);\">No</span> to <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 153, 51);\">Yes</span> or vise versa.</li></ul><ul><li>Average Rating column is the total average rating of the moderator on a particular category.<br></li></ul><ul><li>If the assigned member don\'t want to be notified, click on the icon under Notify column and the icon will be changed from <a href=\"index.php?option=com_jtickets&controller=ticket-projectmembers&task=notify&uid=100&pjid=300&notify=1&titleheader=jAffiliates\"><img src=\"../joobi/user/themes/admin/joobi/images/toolbar/16/sendm.png\"></a> to <a href=\"index.php?option=com_jtickets&controller=ticket-projectmembers&task=notify&uid=2288&pjid=300&notify=0&titleheader=jAffiliates\"><img src=\"../joobi/user/themes/admin/joobi/images/toolbar/16/sendmno.png\"></a>.</li><li>These notification emails are when a customer created a ticket, a reply or re-assign a ticket to his/her.<br></li></ul><br>','1','1253278002FXOA'),('See the list of moderators','1','1253278008KTBE'),('Tips/Guidelines','1','1253693139FSTT'),('Assigned Categories','1','1253939296HYAU'),('This view list all the moderators in assigning a category.<br><ul><li>You can filter the list of moderators by selecting the role of moderators in the drop down list.<br></li></ul><br>','1','1253939297EESY'),('To view the category assigned to a certain moderator','1','1253939300OXBL'),('Go back to the list of moderators','1','1253939300OXBM'),('Specify the number of support level you want to have.','1','1254902067FPJK'),('Referring name of your category. This cannot be edited anymore, so it\'s better to put a descriptive name.','1','1254973731GJXK');
