he relative of all data.</span></li></ul>','1','1271935568TCVD'),('This view is the Report on No. of Tickets each Category. <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">By default, the report is generated by interval of Weekly of This Month range.</span><br><ul><li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">To change the date range of the generated report</span>, select the range in thedrop down list then it will automatically generated the report.</li><li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">To generate a report on a specific date</span>, select the start and end date in the specified date group, then click generate button.</li><li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">You can <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">filter the report by selecting values in the drop down list of Ticket types and/or Ticket status.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Report Type</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> radio list is to change the view of report whether to display data in </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Graph or Data Listing.</span><br></li></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0);\">NOTE:</span><br><ul><li>Click <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Refresh</span> Button to load the page again, if you change the selected intervals.</li><li>The <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Reference Time</span> is the <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Time Zone in the Local Settings of your Joomla Website Configuration.</span></li></ul>','1','1271935568TCVE'),('The email inputted does not match the email address of the author!','1','1274840559DZKC'),('Inform the first assigned moderator when a ticket has been re-assigned to another moderator by sending a notification email.<br><br>','1','1274840563ACFV'),('Notify the first assigned moderator that a reply is made by the author of the ticket.<br>','1','1274840563ACFW'),('Inform first assigned moderator','1','1274840563ACFY'),('Notify first assigned moderator','1','1274840563ACFZ'),('Click YES, if you want the first assigned moderator follow-ups the ticket when assigned to other moderator.<br><br>','1','1274853994MOVS'),('Follow-up the ticket','1','1274853995IMCH'),('check if the ticket is already read','1','1275546208KHTH'),('check if ticket is read or not','1','1275546208KHTI'),('An error occured while saving your email address, please try again.','1','1298350701PQGH'),('Last Post','1','1301972449PYGW'),('Posted By: ','1','1301972449PYGX'),('Number of Posts','1','1301972449PYGY'),('Number of Sub Topics','1','1301972449PYGZ'),('New Topic','1','1301972467EVBQ'),('My Topics','1','1301972467EVBR'),('Sub Topics','1','1301972476PCKS'),('Topic Nested','1','1301972484PNWJ'),('List of Topics','1','1301972485LRRR'),('Ticket type','1','1302521419ICOC'),('<p>This view shows all the categories.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You can Add, Edit or Delete a category.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 255)\">Assign</span>: This link allows you to assign moderators to a category.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 255)\">Tickets</span>: This link allows you to see all the tickets submitted for that category.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 255)\">Canned Replies:</span> This link allows you to see all the list of possible replies on a certain issues submitted in the ticket.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 255)\">NOTE</span>: Please don&#39;t delete the category named \"Default Category\".</p>','1','1302868720HXKT'),('Cannot Assign Ticket! You are the only moderator on this project.','1','1303289070EWBD'),('','1','1304525968YBL'),('Previous Tickets','1','1306127237JGYC'),('Customer Tickets','1','1306127247PKPG'),('Modifiedby','1','1310007858PLWN'),('You need to turn on the preference Tickets by email!','1','1325527934LWRY'),('subscribe','1','1329161820RPTN'),('Ticket ID is Empty','1','1330529258DZNE'),('Your reply is too short!','1','1330529258DZNF'),('The ticket cannot be assigned because there is only one Support Agent assigned to this category.','1','1330529258DZNG'),('Default privacy settings','1','1330529264IHSD'),('Forum like','1','1330529264IHSE'),('No reply yet!','1','1339527673WLQ'),('Allow file upload','1','1340214246QLDQ'),('Yes to allow user to upload files.','1','1340214246QLDR'),('Rolid','1','1347652452OQAE'),('Knowledge Base','1','1361919649HLBV'),('Select category','1','1361919649HLBW'),('Select status','1','1361919650QJLA'),('Select type','1','1361919650QJLB'),('Tktypeid','1','1361919652QSMD'),('The name is shown to the user.<br>','1','1361919656JBOJ'),('The alias is only shown to the Support Manager<br>','1','1361919656JBOK'),('Block Spammers','1','1369750812CTEV'),('Notify of Spammers','1','1369750812CTEW'),('Bad words filter','1','1369750812CTEX'),('Spam filter','1','1369750812CTEY'),('Yes, to block users whose post are flagged as spam.<br>','1','1369750812CTEZ'),('Yes, to notify the Support Manager of Spammers. The manager will receive an email with information about the spammer, the spam post and link to unblock the user if necessary.<br>','1','1369750812CTFA'),('Define a list of bad words considered as spam.<br>Separate each expression by a comma.<br>If any of those words are found in the post, the words are replaced by ****.<br>','1','1369750812CTFB'),('Define a list of bad words considered as spam.<br>Separate each expression by a comma.<br>If any of those words are found in the post, the post is unpublished automatically.<br>','1','1369750812CTFC'),('In progress','1','1373466832FDPH'),('To save and assign ticket','1','1376432916NMHS'),('This task will trigger when you want to save the reply and re-assign the ticket to another moderator at the same time.<br>','1','1376432916NMHT'),('Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid}','1','1380065050EKTP'),('({widget:param|name=priority})Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} for {widget:param|name=category}','1','1380065050EKTQ'),('Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} for {widget:param|name=category}','1','1380065050EKTR'),('Unsolved Ticket [{widget:param|name=ticketid}]','1','1380065050EKTS'),('({widget:param|name=priority}) Support required for ticket [{widget:param|name=ticketid}] of category {widget:param|name=category}','1','1380065050EKTT'),('Unanswered Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid}','1','1380065050EKTU'),('Unpaid Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid}','1','1380065050EKTV'),('Not enough credits for Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} response','1','1380065050EKTW'),('Response for Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid}','1','1380065050EKTX'),('Copy of reply you created in the Ticket [{widget:param|name=ticketid}]','1','1380065050EKTY'),('Ticket [{widget:param|name=ticketid}] has been re-assigned','1','1380065050EKTZ'),('Duplicate Copy: Ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} for {widget:param|name=category}','1','1380065050EKUA'),('Hello {widget:name},\r\n\r\nThis is an automated message, please do not reply. This confirm that your ticket has been recorded.  The ticket number is {widget:param|name=ticketid} .\r\n\r\n{widget:param|name=link}\r\n\r\nPlease be patient and do not submit multiple requests for the same question.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n{widget:sitename}','1','1380065050EKUB');
INSERT IGNORE INTO `#__translation_en` (`text`,`auto`,`imac`) VALUES ('A ticket has been submitted for the category {widget:param|name=category}.\r\n\r\nTitle: {widget:param|name=title}.\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\n\r\n{widget:param|name=link}','1','1380065050EKUC'),('A reply has been recorded for the ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} (category {widget:param|name=category}.\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\n\r\n{widget:param|name=link}','1','1380065050EKUD'),('Hello {widget:name},\r\n\r\nThis is an automated message, please do not reply. A reply has been recorded for your ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid}.\r\n\r\nLink:\r\n{widget:param|name=link}\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\n{widget:sitename} Team','1','1380065050EKUE'),('Hi,\r\n\r\nYou still have ticket [{widget:param|name=ticketid}] which is still unsolved. If you want to close this ticket automatically, click this link {widget:param|name=linkclose}.\r\n\r\nTicket information\r\n\r\nTitle: {widget:param|name=title}\r\nCreated: {widget:param|name=created}\r\nBy: {widget:param|name=author}\r\nStatus: {widget:param|name=status}\r\n\r\nLast reply: {widget:param|name=lastreply}\r\n\r\nLink to view the Ticket:\r\n{widget:param|name=link}','1','1380065050EKUF'),('Hi,\r\n\r\nYour support is required to solve the ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} of category {widget:param|name=category}. This ticket is assigned by {widget:param|name=assignedby}.\r\n\r\n\r\nTicket information:\r\n\r\nTitle: {widget:param|name=title}\r\nCreated: {widget:param|name=created}\r\n\r\n\r\nLink: {widget:param|name=link}\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\n','1','1380065050EKUG'),('Hello {widget:name}\r\n\r\nHereafter is a list of tickets which have been automatically closed due to lack of response.  If you consider the issue solved, you have nothing to do.\r\nHowever if the issue is not yet solved then you can re-open the ticket at any time.\r\n\r\n{widget:param|name=message}\r\n\r\nTicket information\r\n\r\nList of tickets:\r\n\r\n{widget:param|name=ticketids}','1','1380065050EKUH'),('Hello {widget:name}\r\n\r\nWe have not received any response back from you for ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} in the last {widget:param|name=delaywarning} days, and would like to know if you consider this issue to be resolved.\r\n\r\nPlease note that the ticket will automatically be closed in {widget:param|name=closein} days if no response is received from you. The Ticket will not be closed in the case that you send another reply.\r\n\r\nLink:\r\n{widget:param|name=link}\r\n{widget:param|name=linkclose}\r\n\r\nTitle:\r\n{widget:param|name=title}\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPowered by Joobi','1','1380065050EKUI'),('Hi Support,\r\n\r\nUnpaid ticket has been submitted for the project  {widget:param|name=project}.\r\n\r\nTitle:\r\n{widget:param|name=title}\r\n\r\nLink:\r\n{widget:param|name=link}\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\nPlease don\'t reply though unless it is paid.\r\n\r\nThank You','1','1380065050EKUJ'),('Hello {widget:name},\r\n\r\nHere is a copy of your reply created for the Ticket: {widget:param|name=ticketid}.\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\n\r\nKind Regards,\r\n{widget:sitename} Team\r\n\r\n\r\n','1','1380065050EKUK'),('Hi {widget:name},\r\n\r\nThe ticket you are handling has been re-assigned to another moderator named, {widget:param|name=newmoderator}.\r\nTo view the ticket, follow this link {widget:param|name=link}.\r\n\r\nFor a brief summary, here\'s the content of the ticket:\r\nTitle:\r\n{widget:param|name=title}\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\n\r\n','1','1380065050EKUL'),('Hi {widget:name},\r\n\r\nThis is to inform you that the ticket which was assigned to you, a new reply has been recorded. To view the ticket, follow this link, {widget:param|name=link}.\r\n\r\nHere are the following information of the ticket:\r\n\r\nCategory Name:\r\n{widget:param|name=category}\r\n\r\nTicket ID:\r\n{widget:param|name=ticketid}\r\n\r\n\r\nContent:\r\n{widget:param|name=description}\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','1','1380065050EKUM'),('<p>Hello {widget:name},<br /><br />This is an automated message, please do not reply. This confirm that your ticket has been recorded. The ticket number is {widget:param|name=ticketid} .<br /><br /><span style=\"font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;\">Link:</span><br />{widget:param|name=link}<br /><br /><span style=\"font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;\">Title:</span><br />{widget:param|name=title}<br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;\">Content:</span><br />{widget:param|name=description}<br /><br />Please be patient and do not submit multiple requests for the same question.<br /><br />Thank you.<br />{widget:sitename}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>','1','1380065050EKUN'),('<p>Hello {widget:name}<br /><br />Hereafter is a list of tickets which have been automatically closed due to lack of response. If you consider the issue solved, you have nothing to do.<br />However if the issue is not yet solved then you can re-open the ticket at any time.<br /><br />{widget:param|name=message}<br /><br /><span style=\"font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;\">List of Tickets:</span><br /><br />{widget:param|name=ticketids}<br /><br /><br /></p>','1','1380065050EKUU'),('<p>Hello {widget:name},</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>You have received a response for your ticket {widget:param|name=ticketid} and your credit had been deducted.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">Remaining Credits</span>:</span> {widget:param|name=credits}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>To Add more credits {widget:param|name=link2}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;\">Link</span></p>\r\n<p>{widget:param|name=link}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;\">Content</span></p>\r\n<p>{widget:param|name=description}<br /><br /><br /><br />Kindly,</p>\r\n<p>{widget:sitename} team</p>\r\n<p></p>','1','1380065050EKUY'),('<p>Hi {widget:firstname},<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe ticket you submitted has been assigned to a new agent to better serve you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To view the ticket, follow this link {widget:param|name=link}.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRegards,<br />\r\n{widget:sitename} team</p>\r\n','1','1380065050EKVA'),('<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<p><br />The following user got banned from your website because their used a word that you classified as bad words.</p>\r\n<p>The user profile {widget:param|name=name} has been blocked, so the user can\'t access the website any more.</p>\r\n<p>Name: {widget:param|name=name}</p>\r\n<p>Username: {widget:param|name=username}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>If you think this is a mistake you can manually unblock this user here:</p>\r\n<p>{widget:param|name=profileLink}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>The post which contain the \"Bad Words\" has been unpublished.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>','1','1380065050EKVC'),('Tickets Preferences','1','1380567700MUPJ'),('Disable Type','1','1389742176NZPI'),('Edit Close ticket','1','1389742176NZPJ'),('Click yes to allow moderator to have a signature.<br><br>','1','1389742176NZPK'),('Plan','1','1389879775LPOL'),('Click here to view the ticket','1','1389884098SHJK'),('Use Rating','1','1389884105BXKZ'),('Allow others to see the rating','1','1389884105BXLA'),('Display IP','1','1389884105BXLB'),('Only customers IP','1','1389884105BXLC'),('Display status','1','1389884105BXLD'),('Only customers status','1','1389884105BXLE'),('Late reply notification','1','1389884105BXLF'),('Notify on late reply','1','1389884105BXLG'),('Late delay','1','1389884105BXLH'),('Notify c