ted with a specific frequency ( for example every Day ) or at a specific date in the future.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>How does it work?</strong><br />\r\nTo launch those scheduled tasks, the scheduler needs to be triggered by something...</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Any visit on your website can trigger the system (so no visit means no task run!)<br />\r\n	In that case you have to turn ON the option \"User Cron System\".</li>\r\n	<li><strong>OR</strong> an <a href=\"http://www.joobi.co/index.php?option=com_jlinks&controller=redirect&link=trigger_jscheduler\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">external system can trigger the scheduler</a> application by accessing the url :\r\n	<div><strong>{widget:site}index.php?option=com_jcenter&controller=scheduler&task=process&tmpl=component&password=</strong></div>\r\n\r\n	<div><em>(enter the password if you have set one. Copy/paste this url on your browser to see if the scheduler application get launched properly)</em></div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	This second solution is recommended as the system will be launched at fixed dates and won&#39;t depend on your website traffic.<br />\r\n	In that case you can turn OFF the option \"User Cron System\".</li>\r\n</ul>','1','1380037279FKRS'),('Direct Edit Modules','1','1381500332FVXY'),('Enables to directly edit modules from the front-end of the site.','1','1381500333LIEA'),('Default Editor Back-end','1','1385472707OHUT'),('Default Editor Front-End','1','1385472707OHUU'),('Default WYSIWYG editor for users in the back-end.<br>','1','1385472708HAZN'),('Update All Apps','1','1389123468CKOO'),('Need update','1','1389125413BAER'),('The API key entered does not exist.','1','1389275707OUAK'),('The application information could not be updated with the API key received.','1','1389275708EKXJ'),('API key','1','1389275714NKEJ'),('Please enter your API key.','1','1389275715RJLN'),('Enter API key','1','1389275715RJLO'),('Enter Your API key','1','1389275716SJHL'),('Problem of communication with the distribution server!