efault.</p>','1','1271819049DNZB'),('Origin','1','1273655191NLYX'),('Clone','1','1298294078HATF'),('Main Files','1','1298294079SVND'),('Successfully saved the file $file','1','1298294183ETWL'),('Kindly enter a folder name','1','1298350435GKOB'),('The folder \"$folder\" already exists. Kindly enter another folder name.','1','1298350435GKOC'),('do we need to customize only one item that can be set as default?','1','1298350436LSKP'),('Folder name','1','1298350437HNTL'),('Clone Theme','1','1298350437HNTN'),('Theme main files','1','1298350437HNTO'),('Theme custom view  files','1','1298350437HNTP'),('Theme stylesheet files','1','1298350437HNTQ'),('Theme js files','1','1298350437HNTR'),('Theme Edit File','1','1298350437HNTS'),('Upload a theme','1','1298350438DLWR'),('Column 1','1','1298350843FMVJ'),('Column 2','1','1298350843FMVK'),('<p><strong>Information Tab:</strong> Short information about the theme<br />\r\n<strong>General Design Tab:</strong> You can define the general look and feel of all Application in the backend and front-end. This option is accessible through <strong>Joomla 3.2 Responsive Admin Theme</strong>.<br />\r\n<strong>Catalog Design Tab:</strong> You can customize different options to change the look and feel of your store such as button color, sizes and icons. This option is accessible through <strong>Joomla 3.2 Responsive Theme</strong>.</p>','1','1300111184CKDD'),('<p>For more information about HTML, css, etc., kindly refer to this <a href=\"http://www.w3schools.com/html/html_examples.asp\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HTML, CSS Documentation\">documentation</a>.</p>','1','1300169727QALO'),(' Name','1','1300366591QTAJ'),(' Thumbnail','1','1300366591QTAK'),('Select Theme','1','1300366596LVYZ'),('Enter the destination folder.<br><br><br>','1','1301400667SKBF'),('Copy Theme','1','1301400668NOSW'),('','1','1304525968YBL'),('Add File','1','1306927257COUB'),('File Type','1','1306927259HYXV'),('Cart','1','1307002587NUOA'),('File already exists.','1','130700597