398536329FXPL'),('If you want to list specific items list them here. Separate item IDs with comma. IDs can be either numeric or or identifier of the item or the SKU of the product.<br>If you want to EXCLUDE a item simply put a minus sign (-) before the ID and NO space ( eg: -myitem ).<br>','1','1398536330MSXC'),('Specify the remote category ID that you want to fetch.<br>The category ID can either be the numeric ID or Identifier. You can identify the category ID by looking at the number \"eid\" in the URL.<br>','1','1398536330MSXD'),('If you want to list specific vendors, list them here. Separate vendor IDs with comma. IDs can be either numeric or email or the identifier of the vendor.<br>If you want to EXCLUDE a vendor simply put a minus sign (-) before the ID NO space ( eg: -myvendor ).<br>','1','1398536331HTAG'),('Enter here the identifier for the item type.<br>','1','1398536332RVRR'),('Enter here a UNIQUE name for this category. This identifier should not contain spaces or special characters.','1','1398536333LSOF'),('If you want to list specific categories, list them here. Separate category IDs with comma. IDs can be either numeric or the identifier of the category.<br>If you want to EXCLUDE a category simply put a minus sign (-) before the ID NO space ( eg: -mycategory ).<br>','1','1398536333LSOG'),('Here\'s the product types defined for your store.<br><ul><li><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Name</span> - name of the product type.</li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Identifier</span> - identifier of the product type ( admin perspective ).</li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Description</span> - information regarding the product type.</li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Author</span> - creator of the product type.</li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Assigned</span> - pop up that contains the list of the products assigned to the product type.</li></ul><ul><li>You can create/add a new type by clicking on the \"<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">New</span>\" button.</li><li>You can edit a type by clicking it on its name under the \"<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Name</span>\" column or by clicking on the \"<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Edit</span>\" button.</li><li>You can delete a type by clicking on the \"<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Delete</span>\" button.</li><li>You can show/remove this wizard/tips by clicking the \"<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Wizard</span>\" button.</li></ul>','1','1398536334FJGJ'),('Upload a csv file to be able to import products from a file.<br><br>In the csv file, the first line/headings should be the columns where you want to insert the data.<br>The headings must be separated by a comma with no spaces. e.g. <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">name</span>, <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">description</span>, etc.<br><br>Then for the rest of the content, each line is for one product and must also be separated with a comma with no spaces. Futhermore, they should be placed inside a quote(\"\"). <br><br>List of possible headings:<br><ul><li>name (required and the only column that is required to be able to import)</li><li>introduction</li><li>alias</li><li>description</li><li>curid</li><li>comment</li><li>price</li><li>publish</li><li>featured</li><li>stock</li><li>biddingstart - (for auction)<br></li><li>biddingend - (for auction)</li><li>startingbid - (for auction)</li><li>reservebid - (for auction)</li><li>availablestart - (for auction)</li><li>availableend - (for auction)</li><li>publishstart - (for auction)</li><li>publisheend - (for auction)</li><li>private - (for auction)</li><li>auto - (for auction)</li></ul>You may also put other headings that we\'ll be needing to be able to determine other columns. e.g. <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">currency</span> for curid(incase you don\'t know the curid) for the currency please provide the 3 letter code, e.g. EUR for Euro, USD for US dollars, etc.<br><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">priceType</span> for priceid(e.g. standard, donation, etc.)<br><br>You may also put the heading <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">type</span> to determine that the data in one row that you are about to import is either a product, subscription, auction, etc.<br><br>Add a <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">category</span> heading too, to be able to upload the products in a specific category. Please use the identifier of a category.<br><br>You can also add, the headings, <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">imageFile</span> and provide the filename for the image of the product, <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">productFile</span> and provide the filename of the product for download and <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">previewFile</span> and provide the filename of the product for the preview .<br><br>Please also provide the path for the product image, product download file and for the product preview file in the fields below. These 3 paths can be the same.<br><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 153);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 153);\">Note: Only import a csv file.</span><br>','1','1398536334FJGK'),('Show Arrows','1','1399569022HAOL'),('Price Type','1','1400007137KLSS'),('End Publishing','1','1400007137KLST'),('Start Purchase','1','1400007137KLSU'),('End Purchase','1','1400007137KLSV'),('Preview File','1','1400007137KLSW'),('Item File','1','1400007137KLSX'),('Define if the terms and conditions should be shared with vendors.','1','1400790940DZZP'),('Define who can edit the terms and conditions.','1','1400790940DZZQ'),('Automatic Item address','1','1401197990PNXP'),('If the address of the item is not defined, the address will be automatically populated with the address of the vendor.<br>','1','1401197992AJGM'),('Yes to show the navigation arrows on the carrousel.<br>','1','1401838636JZWK'),('Points','1','1402406546FPGB'),('Choose Location','1','1404269826PSKU'),('Background','1','1404269838EWWV'),('Border color','1','1404269838EWWX'),('Use Item Promotion','1','1404269838EWWY'),('Yes to use advance featured Item functionality also called Item Promotion. It allows to define specifically where an item get promoted and the promotion looks like.','1','1404269841LWXW'),('CSS Style','1','1404309375CJFS'),('Yes, define that the item should be featured at the top of the list.<div>Otherwise the item will be simply highlighted in the list.</div>','1','1404309377LEAS'),('Define any other CSS style which should be applied.','1','1404309377LEAT'),('Choose a style','1','1405045348TJCI'),('Points that the feature cost.','1','1405045354CHHU'),('Duration in days','1','1405045354CHHV'),('Hot','1','1405139915GGBP'),('Sale','1','1405139918JIDN'),('You do not have enough points to promote your item.<br />Please add points and try again to promote the item.','1','1405139921HXZR'),('Click here to $SUBSCRIBE_LINK and add points!','1','1405139921HXZS'),('Standard Square','1','1405139925CTSX'),('Standard Circle','1','1405139925CTSY'),('Standard Top-Rounded','1','1405139925CTSZ'),('Etiquette Vertical','1','1405139925CTTA'),('Etiquette Horizontal','1','1405139925CTTB'),('Ribbon Vertical','1','1405139925CTTC'),('Ribbon Horizontal','1','1405139925CTTD'),('Top - Right','1','1405139925CTTE'),('Top Left','1','1405139925CTTF'),('Bottom Left','1','1405139925CTTG'),('Bottom Right','1','1405139925CTTH'),('Badge color','1','1405139930SCQX'),('Badge Name','1','1405139930SCQY'),('Badge Position','1','1405139930SCQZ'),('Use Paid Promotion','1','1405139930SCRA'),('New Items','1','1405139930SCRB'),('Badge Style','1','1405139930SCRC'),('Badge Color','1','1405139930SCRD'),('Use On Sale Badge','1','1405139930SCRE'),('Use New Item Badge','1','1405139930SCRF'),('Use Featured Badge','1','1405139930SCRG'),('Specify an item unique Identifier<br>','1','1405139931GSLV'),('An alias for your own record. This is not displayed to the user.','1','1405139934GAIG'),('Define any CSS class that should be applied.','1','1405139934GAIH'),('The name for the feature. It will be displayed to the vendor.','1','1405